        "The research question specifies 'oarfish-quantified long-read RNA-seq samples' and the 'type=\"oarfish\"' parameter, but the paper does not mention oarfish as a supported quantification tool. The paper discusses Salmon, kallisto, RSEM, Cufflinks, and Bit Seq as quantification sources compatible with tximport.",
