      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "The paper does not discuss inferential replicates, Gibbs samples, bootstrap samples, or the propagation of quantification uncertainty through tximport. The paper focuses on importing transcript-level abundance estimates and using average transcript length offsets for DGE analysis. No mention of 'divide=TRUE', 'DGEListFromTximport', or overdispersion estimation via inferential replicates appears in any passage.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-12688-f1000research-7563-1",
