      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "we provide an R package ( tximport) to help users integrate transcript-level abundance estimates from common quantification pipelines into count-based statistical inference engines... tximport, to import transcript lengths and abundance estimates from several popular quantification packages and export (estimated) count matrices and, optionally, average transcript length correction terms (i.e., offsets)",
      "asbval:note": "tximport functionality is explicitly described in abstract and methods.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-12688-f1000research-7563-1",
